snippet.title: Arclands Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Please support the game on KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/jonkellerdev/arclands

Being the Head Wizard of a settlement is not easy. Help your citizens to survive and thrive in the treacherous Arclands in this RPG inspired city builder.

Music by the fantastic Adam Bow:
https://www.bowadam.com/

Want to stay up to date with the project? Consider following me on social media:

Twitter https://twitter.com/jonkellerdev
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/jonkellerdev/
Itch.io https://jonkeller.itch.io/
Discord: https://discord.gg/arclands
